    "id": "component:blog-constructor:promptsignin:props",
    "section_title": "Props",
    "content": "Props for PromptSignIn:\n\n- onClickSignIn: React.EventHandler<React.SyntheticEvent> — Callback when the sign-in button is clicked\n- actions: PromptAction[] — Custom action buttons. Defaults to a single sign-in button\n- className: string — Additional CSS class\n- message: string — Prompt message text. Defaults to a localized sign-in prompt\n- title: string — Prompt title text"
  },
